  <md:title>How to Deserve a Property Right</md:title>
  <md:abstract>Ronald Coase is famous for his observations about who would get what when property rights overlap with each other, but an important question that he doesn't talk about, is who deserves what. In this video, Professor Dan Russell of the University of Arizona applies insights from Coase’s work on property rights to answer the question of how people deserve property rights.</md:abstract>
